*HEADING
Minimal cantilever brick for AIENG real-ccx smoke test.
Single C3D8 element. Fixed at x=0, point load at x=1.
Intended only for verifying that the external CalculiX adapter
(cae.run_solver) can execute a real ccx process and write
result.frd back into the .aieng package.
No mesh generation, no input deck generation, and no physical
correctness validation is performed by AIENG.
